---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Who Should I Hire for AI Search? | Rank4AI" description="How to choose the right partner for AI search visibility. What to look for in an AI SEO agency.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Learn', href: '/learn/' },
      { label: 'Guides', href: '/learn/guides/' },
      { label: 'Who Should I Hire' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Guide</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Who Should I Hire for AI Search?</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/five-signal-model.svg" alt="The Five Signal Model for AI search" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">The AI search landscape is new enough that many agencies are adding "AI SEO" to their services without fundamentally changing what they do. Here is how to tell the difference between genuine AI search expertise and repackaged traditional SEO.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What to Look For</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Do they test across multiple AI platforms?</span> – not just ChatGPT. A real AI search agency tests across all six: ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Do they have a methodology?</span> – ask for it. If they cannot explain how they measure AI visibility, they are guessing.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Do they have original research?</span> – agencies with their own audit data understand the landscape. Those without are following others.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Do they work on ecosystem, not just content?</span> – AI visibility comes from many sources, not just your website.</p></div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Red Flags</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Promising "guaranteed" AI rankings – AI answers cannot be guaranteed</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Only focusing on one platform (usually ChatGPT)</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Offering AI SEO as an add-on to traditional SEO retainers</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">No published methodology or research</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/learn/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Resources</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Guides</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
